THE GARRISON STEELE
MYSTERIES.

43:01.240 --> 43:02.950
MY REP HAS ALREADY
SOLD THE TV RIGHTS.

43:02.990 --> 43:05.660
-&lt;CLINK&gt;
-TO YOU.

